## Why We Made This

Because the defaults are broken.

Because too much gets scraped, remixed, monetized, and shoved into closed loops without a trace of the original hands that shaped it.

Because openness without protection isnâ€™t generosityâ€”itâ€™s abandonment.

The commons needs guardrails. Not for hoarding, but for remembering where things came fromâ€”and who still cares.

